Class EjbWSAdapter

  • public class EjbWSAdapter
extends org.glassfish.grizzly.servlet.ServletHandler
    This class extends the ServletAdapter and sets the servletInstance to the EjbWebServiceServlet so that its service method is invoked whenever a request maps to this Adapter
